{"tid":1173270,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"宜家仲有冇人屙屎會攞埋本八卦雜誌入去睇？","createTime":"2019-05-27T03:52:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-29T15:41:38.000Z","uid":15933,"like":34,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"e2a4be5ebc1c7d7b906335ac7aa2d3dc499da2ce","tid":1173270,"uid":15933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T03:52:56.000Z","msg":"以前屋企廁所永遠有幢雜誌/老夫子漫畫係到，方便屙屎嗰陣解悶。宜家莫講話雜誌，連報紙都好少買<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以前一放學要做功課就急唔急屎都會死入廁所偷懶當差差電，一邊睇老夫子一邊醞釀情緒去廁所，呢種感覺好正 ，係一個人嘅小天地<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />同睇電話好唔同，我諗呢個永遠係童年嘅回憶 宜家唔會再有偷懶唔做功課呢個情境  嗰種感覺都唔會再有 唉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：啱啱屙屎冇帶電話入去廁所 所以回憶咗30分鐘站童年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a356b5fcb714bff195aacd8e2a05349d3179ca7f","tid":1173270,"uid":15933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T04:05:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />竟然冇人屙屎睇雜誌"},{"pid":"380b14c9bd0813319c1a949ca4332fb9793de7a9","tid":1173270,"uid":147789,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T04:09:04.000Z","msg":"而家仲邊有人會屙屎"},{"pid":"417a224bd73961e9724e75c35004fc3eea932687","tid":1173270,"uid":15933,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"380b14c9bd0813319c1a949ca4332fb9793de7a9","tid":1173270,"uid":147789,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T04:09:04.000Z","msg":"而家仲邊有人會屙屎"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T08:21:11.000Z","msg":"靚仔靚女先唔屙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1e3ce4cece659bf556c68983c01d45c4499ffe6","tid":1173270,"uid":147789,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"417a224bd73961e9724e75c35004fc3eea932687","tid":1173270,"uid":15933,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"380b14c9bd0813319c1a949ca4332fb9793de7a9","tid":1173270,"uid":147789,"like":35,"disl